    • parse

      public void parse(ca.uhn.hl7v2.model.Segment segment)
      Parse a segment for a message. This method will be called by MessageParser for each segment of the given type that appears within the method. It will create the primary resource produced by the parser and then parses individual fields of the segment and passes them to parser methods to add them to the primary resource or to create any extra resources.
      Overrides:
      parse in class AbstractStructureParser
      Parameters:
      segment - The segment to be parsed
